item.title: CVE-2023-41368|2024-09-26T16:04:32.037Z -- sap_se -- s4%20hana%20abap%20%28manage%20checkbook%20apps%29
item.description: The OData service of the S4 HANA (Manage checkbook apps) - versions 102, 103, 104, 105, 106, 107, allows an attacker to change the checkbook name by simulating an update OData call.
